        <item>
            <title>Google Veo 2 免费生成 AI 影片教学，输入文字即可生成 8 秒影片</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/21/google-veo-2/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-veo-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/21/google-veo-2/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 21 Apr 2025 04:20:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[实用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[应用软件]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1304318</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今时今日除了用 AI 绘制图片，一般平民大众也可用免费工具生成 AI 影片，制作 AI 电影已不是梦想。Google AI Studio 近日正式推出 Veo 2 模型，只需简单的文字描述，便能轻松生成高品质短片。以下就简单介绍 Google Veo 2 生成影片的做法。</p><p>点击 <a href="https://ai.google.dev/">Google AI Studio</a> 进入网页，这里是一个集成多种 AI 功能的平台。在香港，你需要透过 VPN 才可使用 Google AI Studio。</p><h2>步骤 1：进入 Google AI Studio 并登入帐户</h2><p>进入 Google AI Studio 网站后点击页面上的「Explore models in Google AI」按钮，再按「Try Gemini」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042134726-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304326" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042134726-694x417.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="417" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042134726-694x417.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042134726-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042134742-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304327" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042134742-694x404.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="404" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042134742-694x404.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042134742-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>步骤 2：切换到 Veo 2 影片生成功能</h2><p>登入后，进入 Google AI Studio 工作区，从左侧选单中选择「Video Gen」选项，即可切换到 Veo 2 影片生成区域。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250421_3_482_10-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304328" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250421_3_482_10-694x400.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="400" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250421_3_482_10-694x400.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250421_3_482_10-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>步骤 3：上传图片或输入文字描述</h2><p>最简单的用法是，输入一句甚至一段文字描述来生成图片。</p><p>例如输入：「在一块木砧板上，厨师以熟练的刀法切牛扒，一块一块地切出来」</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042141623.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304319" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042141623-694x543.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="543" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042141623-694x543.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042141623.jpg 1150w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>另一个例子是输入「街道上有一辆红色跑车在行驶」，就会生成这样的影片：</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042135055.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304324 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042135055-648x580.jpg" alt="" width="648" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042135055-648x580.jpg 648w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042135055.jpg 1006w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 648px" /></a></p><p>你可修正文字描述而得到其他效果。例如叫跑车在红绿灯前停下。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042135236.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304325 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042135236-694x505.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="505" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042135236-694x505.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042135236.jpg 1238w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>输入自己的图片／相片转换成影片</h2><p>Veo 2 亦可以将静态图片转换为动态影片，按右手边的加入图片按钮，选「Upload Image」，上载相片后，再输入文字描述生成影片。</p><p>例如，输入「在这个场景中有一辆红色的跑车在马路上行驶」，并按下「Run」来生成影片。</p><div class="mceTemp"></div><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042135417.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304322" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042135417-694x412.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="412" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042135417-694x412.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042135417.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042140340.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304323" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042140340-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042140340-694x387.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042140340.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>另一个例子，输入一张香港街道的图片，并生成一段描述「在街道上有一辆红色跑车正在比赛」的影片。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042141210.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304320" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042141210-694x513.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="513" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042141210-694x513.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042141210.jpg 1217w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042141219.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304321" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042141219-694x533.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="533" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042141219-694x533.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042141219.jpg 1172w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>生成的影片会储存到你的 Google Drive，你亦可马上按影片里面右下角的下载按钮，将影片下载到电脑。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/21/google-veo-2/ai/">Google Veo 2 免费生成 AI 影片教学，输入文字即可生成 8 秒影片</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
